---
title: Berbere Chicken & Garlic Rice with Mint Yoghurt & Tomato Salsa
description: Enjoy the mild, aromatic flavours inspired by Ethiopia in a meal that everyone will love! Tender strips of chicken breast get a light Berbere spice coating, which goes perfectly with garlic rice. Then, finish it off with a creamy mint yoghurt to cover all your bases.
